Ive been building a website where you can upload your wardrobe and it gives you outfit suggestions. Today i saw my website idea on Ideabrowser.com, and im going to use it to help me. Bring my website to life, make it fully funtional and go deep. make it using my website as a framework for the frontend, and enhance it to its full potential. here is the full idea browser copy and pasted "Smart Closet App that scans wardrobes and suggests outfits, resale prices, and what to donate
